SIMPLE: overweening
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Overweening
<hw>O`ver*ween"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Unduly confident; arrogant;
presumptuous; conceited.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>O`ver*ween"ingly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos> <au>Milton.</au> -- <wf>O`ver*ween"ing*ness</wf>,
<pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The conceits of warmed or <qex>overweening</qex> brain.</q>
<rj><qau>Locke.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Here's an <qex>overweening</qex> rogue.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Overweening</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Overweening
<hw>O`ver*ween"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Conceit; arrogance.</def>
<rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Overweigh</ent>⟦br⟧
